~ start

Lyra: The air here is heavy... like trying to breathe underwater.
if DialogueState.has_clue("bloody_palm_print")
	Lyra: Wait, I remember this. A bloody palm print. Someone was here recently.
	=> ending
else
	Lyra: The Vestiges are faint. I can't reconstruct anything useful yet.
	=> ending

~ ending
Lyra: I need to keep looking. The Mnemosyne Lattice is hiding something.
=> END
